1.0.name: wordpress/picbox
1.0.description:
This plugin uses Picbox to overlay images on the current page. Picbox is a javascript image viewer that tries to be a bit nicer than all the other lightbox clones, and is designed so it handles larger images with ease. It will automatically scale down images to the browser's screen size, which can then be zoomed into and moved around.
